## Quick Wins Implemented

### ✅ Quick Win #1: Replace Emoji Icons with SVG (2 hours actual)
**Goal:** Replace all emoji icons (📁📂📄📌⭐🗑️) with professional Lucide React SVG icons

**Files Modified:**
- `src/pages/Notes.tsx` (797 lines)
- `src/widgets/NotesEditor.tsx` (minimal import changes)

**Changes:**
```typescript
// BEFORE: Childish emoji icons
<span>{hasChildren ? (isExpanded ? '📂' : '📁') : '📄'}</span>
<span>📌</span>  // Pin
<span>⭐</span>  // Favorite
<button>🗑️</button>  // Delete
<button>⬇️</button>  // Download
<button>📄</button>  // PDF

// AFTER: Professional SVG icons from Lucide
<FolderOpen className="w-4 h-4" />
<Folder className="w-4 h-4" />
<FileText className="w-4 h-4" />
<Pin className="w-4 h-4" />
<Star className="w-4 h-4 fill-amber-500" />
<Trash2 className="w-4 h-4" />
<Download className="w-4 h-4" />
<FileDown className="w-4 h-4" />
```

**Icons Replaced:**
- `▼/▶` → `ChevronDown/ChevronRight`
- `📂/📁/📄` → `FolderOpen/Folder/FileText`
- `✏️` → `Edit2`
- `🗑️` → `Trash2`
- `📌` → `Pin`
- `⭐/☆` → `Star` (filled/outlined)
- `🏷️` → `Tag`
- `✓` → `Check`
- `⬇️` → `Download`
- `⏳/📄` → `Loader2/FileDown` (with animate-spin)
- `📝` → `FileText` (empty state)

**Result:** Professional, consistent icon system with proper sizing (w-4 h-4) and colors.

