### ✅ Quick Win #2: Upgrade Typography System (1 hour actual)
**Goal:** Implement professional typography with Inter font and clear hierarchy

**Files Modified:**
- `index.html` - Added font weight 700
- `src/index.css` - Complete typography system

**Changes:**

**1. Font Import Update:**
```html
<!-- BEFORE -->
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<!-- AFTER -->
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
```

**2. Typography Hierarchy:**
```css
/* Professional Typography Hierarchy */
body {
  font-size: 16px; /* Increased from 14px */
  line-height: 1.5; /* Professional baseline */
}

h1 {
  font-size: 32px;
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.2;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em; /* Tight for large text */
}

h2 {
  font-size: 24px;
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.3;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}

h3 {
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.4;
}

h4 {
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.4;
}

h5, h6 {
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

p {
  line-height: 1.6; /* Tall for readability */
}

strong, b {
  font-weight: 600; /* Medium emphasis */
}

.font-emphasis {
  font-weight: 500; /* Light emphasis */
}
```

**Result:** Clear visual hierarchy, better readability, professional font scaling.

