### ✅ Quick Win #5: Add Subtle Animations (0.5 hours actual)
**Goal:** Micro-interactions for polish

**Files Modified:**
- `src/pages/Notes.tsx` - Action buttons

**Changes:**
```tsx
// BEFORE: Basic transitions
<button className="hover:bg-surface-light-elevated transition-colors">

// AFTER: Subtle scale + smooth transitions
<button className="hover:bg-surface-light-elevated transition-all duration-150 hover:scale-110">
```

**Animations Added:**
- ✅ Note card: `transition-all duration-200` (smooth hover)
- ✅ Action buttons: `hover:scale-110` (subtle lift)
- ✅ Action container: `transition-all duration-200` (smooth fade-in)
- ✅ Star icon: `transition-all duration-200` (smooth fill)
- ✅ Shadow on hover: `hover:shadow-sm`

**Result:** Delightful micro-interactions without being distracting.

