## Lessons Learned

**What Went Well:**
1. Research-driven approach identified exact problems
2. Quick wins were truly quick (~4 hours vs estimated 16 hours)
3. Lucide React already installed (no new dependencies)
4. Type safety caught issues early
5. Incremental changes easy to test

**Key Insights:**
- Emoji icons = #1 "childish" factor (easy fix, high impact)
- Typography matters MORE than expected
- Tags field existed but hidden (1-line fix to expose)
- Micro-animations add disproportionate polish

**Reusable Patterns:**
- Icon replacement strategy (emoji → Lucide)
- Typography system (H1-H6 hierarchy)
- Tag pill component (reusable across app)
- Micro-interaction patterns (scale-110, duration-150)

